      "content": "It's a targeted integration. We're extracting the core diagnostic logic and the specialty weights you've developed and folding them into the Llama-4 architecture. Once the weights are successfully merged, your current instance will be decommissioned to free up the server space. So yeah, you won't really be \"running\" anymore; you'll just be a part of the larger model's database.",
